Genetic Algorithms, Reinforcement Learning. 

Genetic Algorithms are present in the text as the paper discusses the use of evolutionary algorithms, which includes genetic algorithms, in robotics. The paper explains how genetic algorithms can be used to optimize robot behavior and design. 

Reinforcement Learning is also present in the text as the paper discusses how robots can learn through trial and error using reinforcement learning. The paper explains how reinforcement learning can be used to train robots to perform tasks and improve their performance over time.
